# CODEOWNERS — Require reviews for critical file changes
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Workflow files — require security team review
.github/workflows/**    @security-team @devops-team

# Action definitions — require platform team review
**/action.yml           @platform-team

# Dependabot config — require devops team review
.github/dependabot.yml  @devops-team

# Infrastructure files
Dockerfile              @devops-team
docker-compose*.yml     @devops-team
